cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.DS 

This paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) category as it discusses the use of machine learning techniques in online services. It also falls under the Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) category as it proposes a new threat model and discusses strategies to mitigate the risks of linkability attacks. Additionally, it may be categorized under Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) as it deals with user data generated on personal devices. Cybersecurity (cs.CY) and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) are also possible categories as the paper discusses strategies to protect user data and proposes new techniques to identify and match users across devices.
